review 2: What a wonderful viewpoint! Amazing views, and such lovely staff. Good choice of food and drinks. Drive up is slightly steep but our little moped made it with 2 of us on it. Well worth a visit.
review 3: What an amazing experience! Absolute gold! The view is breathtaking and you are in awe as you gaze at the magnificent Gunung Agung. Winata Ketut and staff are beautiful people and the food is delicious, fresh and authentic. Balinese Heaven!
